name: AfriCAN YEBO T-Shirt in White and Red
description:
AfriCAN YEBO T-Shirt in White and Red. A brand new classic in the making featuring a bold but simple YEBO print front and centre. For those of you wondering, YEBO is a Zulu expression of affirmation - that's not so plain English for, YES. It can also be used in response to the greeting, Sawubona.

Classic fit t-shirt equally happy on him or her. Ladies, try a size down to your usual size or size up for a loose-oversized fit.

Ringspun, preshrunk, 100% cotton jersey, crew neck t-shirts.

name: AfriCAN YEBO Ladies T-Shirt in Grey and Denim Blue
description:
AfriCAN YEBO Ladies T-Shirt in Grey and Denim Blue. One for the ladies who want to strut just as hard as the men - this brand new print is a classic in the making featuring a simple YEBO print front and centre. 

For those of you wondering, YEBO is a Zulu expression of affirmation - that's not so plain English for, YES. It can also be used in response to the greeting, Sawubona, i.e HELLO.

Ringspun, preshrunk, 100% cotton jersey, crew neck t-shirts.

name: AfriCAN Warrior Sweatshirt in Cranberry and White
description:
AfriCAN Warrior Sweatshirt in Cranberry and White. Originally printed as a one off t-shirt for a holiday, the AfriCAN Warrior has made a much anticipated comeback by popular demand for the summer. Now available as a summer weight sweatshirt in an all new brilliant cranberry. Featuring a bold AFRICAN WARRIOR print front and centre for you to say it loud and proud. 

The AfriCAN Warrior sweatshirt in cranberry features white ink. Classic raglan sweatshirt, equally happy on him or her. Ladies, try a size down to your usual size.

name: AfriCAN Warrior Artist Series AM T-Shirt in Indigo and White
description:
AfriCAN Warrior Artist Series AM T-Shirt in Indigo and White. 

Creativity and Noise commissions a new artist to create a signature print for the upcoming season. CAN turned to the talented Andrew Mkandla for the first official collaboration and the results were nothing short of spectacular. Unveiled at the 2012 Manchester Carnival, we predict a bright future for a true AfriCAN pioneer. The AfriCAN Warrior Artist Series AM T-Shirt in Indigo features a bold African Warrior print in white front and center and a small AfriCrown print below the rear of the crew neck.

Classic fit t-shirt equally happy on him or her. Ladies, try a size down to your usual size or size up for a loose oversized fit.

Ringspun, preshrunk, 100% cotton jersey, crew neck t-shirts.

name: AfriCrown T-Shirt in Black and Black Pearl
description:
AfriCrown T-Shirt in Grey and Black Pearl. The signature, must have AfriCAN t-shirt from the Creativity and Noise stables. The symbol of your nobility, to be worn and shown off with pride. Ringspun, preshrunk, 100% cotton jersey, crew neck t-shirts.

Classic fit t-shirt equally happy on him or her. Ladies, try a size down to your usual size or size up for a loose oversized fit.

The Crown logo was created as a simple yet chic icon that reflects the brand's design values. The AfriCrown T-Shirt in Grey features a Metallic Black Pearl Crown to the chest a small AfriCrown print below the rear of the crew neck.
